{"tid":2190167,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美拒付6.24億世衞會費 捐同類組織","createTime":"2020-09-05T12:00:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T12:57:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eaf04c526eb21ebb2c83a062100a5f1a42e5f6d2","tid":2190167,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T12:00:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200904/563Z5MFEVFDSRM3OLSARFZT73U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200904%2F563Z5MFEVFDSRM3OLSARFZT73U%2F&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmR%2FZItop%2BIuorIKtd308SUMA%3D&h=3be287ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200904%2F563Z5MFEVFDSRM3OLSARFZT73U%2F&h=b2c916df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200904/563Z5MFEVFDSRM3OLSARFZT73U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美拒付6.24億世衞會費 捐同類組織<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/g28vzKhOX1F7YqkV3x38aSdXKgA=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/R3QEMAPMC5G6BEYHXRQPVYJC3U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fg28vzKhOX1F7YqkV3x38aSdXKgA%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FR3QEMAPMC5G6BEYHXRQPVYJC3U.jpg&h=ee6fbe24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■美國不滿世衞總幹事譚德塞表現。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普早前指摘世界衞生組織（WHO）在武漢肺炎爆發期間擔當中國的傀儡，計劃來年7月6日正式退出，惟尚欠對方8,000萬美元（6.24億港元）會費。國務院官員前日表示美國不會支付這筆費用，將改撥予聯合國的同類組織。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n改撥聯合國同類組織<br />\n<br />\n國務院主管國際組織事務的副助理國務卿庫克（Nerissa Cook）表示，美國尚欠世衞去年1,800萬美元和今年6,200萬美元的會費，這筆資金將用以支付給予聯合國的費用。世衞對美國的決定感到遺憾，將等待更多詳情。<br />\n<br />\n根據1948年的國會決議，美國即使退出世衞，都要繳付現時財政年度的會費，有法律學者批評該決定非法和不道德，認為美國應履行所。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，世衞有份領導的疫苗合作計劃COVAX已有76個富裕國家簽署參與，包括德國、日本和挪威，中國亦有可能加入，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"},{"pid":"5396600832f1cfababaf681494a716e8fefbe9f7","tid":2190167,"uid":230416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T12:01:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d61ee7a07399f6224374473a03603187376c50f5","tid":2190167,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T12:48:51.000Z","msg":"要將佢問吊向世人交代添啦"},{"pid":"c7b83d5e8df9f58b3a9122efb0fee884f1a90493","tid":2190167,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T12:57:54.000Z","msg":"攞多十億出黎棟多支旗好過啦"}]}